'''海菊蛤'''，又稱'''海菊貝'''、'''紅螺'''、'''車蠔'''，是[[海扇蛤目|海扇蛤目]]的其中一[[科|科]]（'''海菊蛤科'''；{{lang|la|'''Spondylidae'''}}），以及此科下唯一的[[屬|屬]]（'''海菊蛤屬'''；{{lang|la|'''''Spondylus'''''}}）。海菊蛤的外觀與[[牡蠣科|牡蠣科]]相似，但其外殼帶有紅色。其殼內之肉可供食用，中國的[[西沙|西沙]]海域盛產的紅螺，特別鮮味<ref>《[[舌尖上的中國|舌尖上的中國]]》</ref>。
海菊蛤物種的型態及分佈範圍差異頗大，但牠們其實與扇貝屬於同一個[[總科|總科]]。與[[牡蠣科|牡蠣科]]物種黏合在岩石上不同，海菊蛤都以[[足絲|足絲]]來固定。
<!-- Their key characteristic is the two parts of their shells are hinged together with a ball-and-socket type of hinge, rather than a toothed hinge as is more common in other bivalves.  They also still retain vestigial anterior and posterior ''auricles'' ("ears", triangular shell flaps) along the hinge line.--><!--

Liks scallops, ''Spondylus'' spp. have multiple eyes around the edges of their shells, and have relatively well-developed [[nervous_system|nervous system]]s.  Their nervous [[ganglion|ganglia]] are concentrated in the [[viscera|viscera]]l region, with recognisable [[optic_lobe|optic lobe]]s connected to the eyes.

''Spondylus'' shells are much sought after by collectors, and a lively commercial market exists in them.-->
